title: On the Go with Joe at Kruger's Corn Cabaret
text: PORTLAND, OR (KPTV) - Joe V. is at Kruger's Farm on Sauvie Island this morning visiting the Corn Cabaret. This is not like any other corn maze. In the middle of the maze, guests will find a carnival featuring fire dancers, live music, outdoor movies and more. To learn more about Kruger's Farm and the Corn Cabaret, visit KrugersFarmMarket.com.
